Enclosing class:
Type
public static class Type.Cache
extends TreeMap

Internal: Cache of all Types in the system. Types are not maintained as singletons, but any call to resolve a classname, Class, etc. will be routed to this master table. It is organized as a map of CacheKey:Type.
